text: 10 Holloway Circus (also called Holloway Circus Tower or Beetham Tower) is a skyscraper in Central Birmingham, England. It is tall, making it the tallest building and second-tallest structure in the city. It is also the 42nd tallest building in the United Kingdom. ==References== Category:Skyscrapers in the United Kingdom Category:Buildings and structures in Birmingham
title: 10 Holloway Circus
